VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT disable_password_authentication\s*=\s*false
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:disable_password_authentication\s*=\s*false && MISSING:# intentional|# development|admin_ssh_key
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Azure Linux VMs with password authentication enabled instead of SSH keys.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Azure VM with Password Authentication Enabled.
